name: My Friend of Misery
wikiSummary: The main melody and opening bass line was written by bassist Jason Newsted.  James Hetfield and Lars Ulrich wrote the rest of the song around Newsted's idea.
wikiText:
The main melody and opening bass line was written by bassist Jason Newsted.  James Hetfield and Lars Ulrich wrote the rest of the song around Newsted's idea.
